      "title": "3 year old child dies after falling into house pond",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 3-year-old child has died after falling into a pet fish pond in a house in the Madhu Kale area in Panvila, police said.",
        "It is suspected that the child fell into the pool while playing in the yard. The body has been placed at the Madukele Hospital. Panvila Police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
